summary: After the events from early today, here is a proper introduction of Sven the Litwick In his original world Sven was just a...
caption:
After the events from early today, here is a proper introduction of Sven the Litwick

In his original world Sven was just a normal litwick, but after crossing the magic mirror to another world against his master’s wishes, he turned into this big man wearing quite a revealing outfit.

He is currently learning how to deal with his new body, and so he is living with Crescente in his coffee shop since he has experience with this kind of situations. He really likes his Master Sven, but he is insecure about he would like or not his new appearence so his existence will be a secret for him from some time.
